Description
Account
Abstract class Account: to be used in Checkings Account and Savings Account

Class ATMSystem: Class containing the menus and data for an ATM.

Class CheckingsAccount: Defines CheckingsAccount object as Account objects which the user should be able to freely withdraw from.
Deposit
Class Deposit: add amount to an account

Class Inquiry: inquire the type and balance of an account
Receipt
Class Receipt: A standard format for a receipt
Request
Class Request: This class represents a transaction request made by the user
SavingsAccount
Class SavingsAccount: An Account object which the user should not be able to freely withdraw from.
Transaction
Abstract class Transaction: This class provides basic functions a transaction has.
